item.title: Need help with my cache
item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

[quote=“rhys132, post:10, topic:423725”][quote author=The Outsider link=topic=526350.msg3834165#msg3834165 date=1322780283]
You should have the cache load from the client and have them download the client/cache as a package (oh wait it’s a web client?)

public static String findCacheDir() {
        return "./cache";
}

Then just rename the cache “cache”, and move it to your client folder (I stated public void findCacheDir, but it was a static String - sorry).

Also, it might be all lower case (findcachedir()).
[/quote]
theres like 4 folders he has to edit,[/quote]
We don’t even know his actual problem. If he just posts it instead of asking for team viewer it could of be a quicker resolve.
